## Getting Started

## Installing

Library can be installed using pip:

```bash
pip install tiny-userpic
```

## Usage

```python
from userpic import make_userpic_image, make_userpic_svg

# make PIL Image object
image = make_userpic_image(
    size=(7, 5),
    padding=(20, 10),
    mode="RGBA",
    image_size=(300, 600),
)
# save as JPEG file
with open("output.jpeg", "wb") as fp:
    image.save(fp)
```

